@Regression @Item_ID_3421429829 @Regression @Item_ID_3421429829_01

Scenario: New Travel request creation and validation using a Arranger login

  • 44
Given user lands on home page of FCM Application with arranger login
When user clicks on create new request button
Then user lands on New Trip Request screen
And user selects a Domestic radio button under travel needs
And select FLIGHTS travel type checkbox and enter no of travellers
And proceeds to the next page by clicking START button
Then user lands on Travel Requirements screen
When user clicks on one way radio button and selects type as Economy
And user selects from and to locations
And proceeds to next page by clicking next button
Then user lands on Administration details screen
When user searches for a traveller and confirms it by clicking confirm button
And user selects reason for travel from the dropdown
And enter extra detail related to your trip and enter segment cost
And checks the Deliver this transaction to Fraedom checkbox
And checks the Where a cost is indicated as 0 in the estimation check box
And user selects Costcollector Employee type and Freedom user License plate from dropdown
And enters the Long Text and clicks on NEXT button
Then Compliance screen should be displayed
When user clicks on IMPORT SPREADSHEET button
Then Import Itinerary popup window gets displayed
And Download template link should be present
When user clicks on Download template link file gets downloaded
And user should be able to upload files using BROWSER FILES button
And complete message should be displayed
And on clicking close icon popup gets closed
And user should be able to ASSIGN to LEAD and notification message should be displayed
When user selects the allocation type from travel diary
And user selects the location and enters the description summary
And clicks on Review button
Then Review trip screen should be displayed
When user captures the Trip Request Id
And Travel dates Maximum budget Reason for travel and Main Travellers should be present
And Data capture & reporting details should be present
And verify Travel Itinerary Details are displayed
And Compliance Details should be present
When user clicks on SEND REQUEST button
Then user should lands on Approvals dashboard screen
And My Pending requests shows the created Trip Request ID
And verify Trip route,Trip dates, Approval,Travellers and Travel types are displayed in pending request preview page
And verify the footer buttons CANCEL PRINT WITHDRAW CHANGE APPROVER RESEND REQUEST are enabled
And verify on clicking Resend request button request gets send successfully
And Notification bar gets displayed with message
And My Pending requests shows the created Trip Request ID
